version 0.0.2
--------------
* ADDED   dialog for displaying the results of a residence time analysis
* ADDED   the user can now select target atoms for the analysis
* ADDED   the tolerance as a parameter of connectivity search
* ADDED   extension for computing atoms in a shell around an atomic center within a given radius
* CHANGED the internal distance units are now in angstrom

version 0.0.1
--------------
* ADDED   bond visualization feature
* CHANGED the various chemical radii stored in the database are now in angstrom

version 0.0.0
--------------
* ADDED GUI
* ADDED Molecular viewer
* ADDED Trajectory reader for PDB and Gro trajectories

